          <enum>(1)</enum>
          <text>by striking <quote>may not be revoked</quote> and all that follows through <quote>and before 2014</quote>, and</text>
        </paragraph>
<paragraph id="H9E8B372D718742CFA05D3ECD58875D26">
          <enum>(2)</enum>
          <text>by striking <quote>
              <header-in-text level="paragraph" style="OLC">irrevocable</header-in-text>
